Global P-Toluenesulfonyl Semicarbazide Foaming Agent Market Insights
P-Toluenesulfonyl Semicarbazide Foaming Agent Market size was valued at USD 0.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.30 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.3% from 2024 to 2030.

P-Toluenesulfonyl Semicarbazide Foaming Agent Market Overview
The global market for P-Toluenesulfonyl Semicarbazide (PTSC) foaming agents has witnessed steady growth due to its increasing application in the production of foamed plastics, especially in the automotive and construction industries. The market value is expected to reach approximately USD 200 million by 2028, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% during the forecast period. PTSC foaming agents are popular for their ability to generate uniform cell structures in various foam applications, making them highly valuable in the manufacturing of lightweight, durable, and insulated products. Key regions driving the growth of this market include North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific.

